{"tid":1651554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中國的會爆炸] 無錫小食店爆炸","createTime":"2019-10-13T11:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T12:24:16.000Z","uid":299537,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"15665268845377d0bd9fab2639965773552133d4","tid":1651554,"uid":299537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:24:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191013/60149183\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191013%2F60149183&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnuYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=4abbc1fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191013%2F60149183&h=250fc7d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191013/60149183</a><br />\n江蘇省無錫市一間小食店今日上午11時許發生爆炸，截至今日下午5時，救援工作結束。經搜救人員點算，事故共造成9人死亡、10人受傷。目前，傷者情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n現場是無錫市錫山區鵝湖鎮新楊路一間小食店，現場閉路電視拍下氣體爆炸的一刻，見威力強勁，煙塵滾滾，街道對面店舖的玻璃亦出現爆裂，多名途經民眾嚇得慌忙躲避。目前當局未有透露事發原因，僅稱現場已進行清理及核實。<br />\n<br />\n當局稱，在醫院的傷者無生命危險，現場的搜救工作已接近尾聲。<br />\n<br />\n一定係爆炸糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc548990e214e7d013db3e42131f85c528a38eb5","tid":1651554,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:26:43.000Z","msg":"天譴"},{"pid":"1155755486128d5f86b4ec9df25b3884025cc07c","tid":1651554,"uid":254246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:27:46.000Z","msg":"kwlc"},{"pid":"ad6a07c302894406f1d9c3373a1072e9be287cf1","tid":1651554,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:32:48.000Z","msg":"原來橋有片"},{"pid":"30202aed65e394021f8dc2be8082008cdfc1f488","tid":1651554,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:35:19.000Z","msg":"天滅中共！"},{"pid":"0bc0d7a25569f3097ab5de2e8505ae53f6144252","tid":1651554,"uid":220182,"like":0,"dislike"